oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Girl at museum
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A young girl, wearing plaid jumper and white shirt with barrette in hair, looks at one of the Bird sketches and paintings at the Children's Museum in Nashville, Tennessee. A drawing of a bird is also in her arms. A stuffed animal is on the bench.
